\c 4
\s Mufaro nerugare zviri kuna Jehovha
\d Kumutungamiriri wenziyo; nemitengeranwa; pisarema raDhavhidhi.
\p
\v 1 Ndipindurei pakudana kwangu, Mwari wekururama kwangu; pakumanikidzwa makapa \add nzvimbo\add* yakafaranuka kwandiri. Ivai nengoni kwandiri, mugonzwa munyengetero wangu\x + Job. 36.16. Map. 66.14.\x*.
\v 2 Imwi vanakomana vevanhu, kusvika rinhi \add muchishandura\add* rukudzo rwangu kuva chinyadzo, muchida zvisina maturo, muchitsvaga nhema? Sera\x + Map. 5.6.\x*.
\v 3 Asi zivai kuti Jehovha wakazvitsaurira\x + Eki. 11.7.\x* anotya Mwari\x + Map. 50.5.\x*; Jehovha anondinzwa pandinodana kwaari.
\v 4 Dederai, murege kutadza\x + VaEfe. 4.26.\x*; tauriranai\x + Map. 77.6.\x* nemoyo wenyu pamubhedha wenyu, uye muve vakanyarara. Sera\x + Map. 149.5.\x*.
\v 5 Ipai zvibairo zvekururama\x + Det. 33.19. Map. 50.14. Map. 51.19.\x*, muvimbe naJehovha\x + Map. 25.2.\x*.
\v 6 Vazhinji vanoti: Ndiani achatiratidza zvakanaka? Jehovha simudzirai\x + Map. 31.16.\x* pamusoro pedu chiedza chechiso chenyu\x + Map. 80.3,7,19. 119.135. Map. 89.15.\x*.
\v 7 Makaisa mufaro mumoyo mangu\x + Isa. 9.3.\x* kupfuura nguva iyo zviyo zvavo newaini itsva yavo zvawanzwa\x + Hos. 2.8.\x*.
\v 8 Ndichazvambarara\x + Job. 17.16.\x* nerugare\x + Job. 11.18,19. Map. 3.5.\x*, ndibve ndabatwa nehope; nokuti imwi moga Jehovha munondigarisa mukuchengetedzeka\x + Rev. 25.18,19. 26.5. Job. 11.18. Det. 12.10.\x*.